==English==
===Hyphenation===
:tam•bour•ine

===Pronunciation===
*[[IPA]]: /ˌtæm.bɝ.ˈ(ɹ)iːn/

===Etymology===
from French [[tambourin]] (lit., "little drum")

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}
# a [[percussion]] [[musical instrument|instrument]] consisting of a small usu. wooden hoop closed on one side with a [[drum]] frame and featuring [[jingle|jingling]] metal disks on the tread; it is usu. held in the hand and shaken [[rhythmic]]ally.

